{"tid":521551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(溏心風暴3) 為收視搏盡宣傳　扔完蛋糕再潑奶茶　啲藝人真係慘","createTime":"2018-01-06T16:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T10:58:48.000Z","uid":156068,"like":5,"dislike":213,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"80bffdf6f706f973ae76dc14cf14a53bf42448db","tid":521551,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"《溏心風暴3》今日又有宣傳活動，連戲份已經完結的唐文龍（Michael）都有出席，大家如果有留意劇集，都知道Michael飾演的角色Nic是一名表面風風光光的壞男人。不過亦無損對Michael的形象，觀眾對他的觀感依然相當之好，令他人氣再度急升。今日出席活動的Michael一樣西裝骨骨，靚靚仔仔出場，點知在台上卻受到大懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n大家還記得，阿Nic在劇中有一幕是被正爸（夏雨飾）潑奶茶，搞到成面都係，那一幕令到觀眾們拍晒手掌。點知今日竟然將當日的劇情重演一次，仲要係真人版即場示範，Michael被潑完都唔知咩事。事後在接受《香港01》訪問時他說：「我都奇怪，點解個蛋糕咁細個，仲要我捧上台，不過估唔到夏雨哥潑奶茶都幾型，仲要都幾準，呢杯奶茶應該係有史以來最好味嘅一杯。」原來呢件事係總監製劉家豪諗出來，目的就係要急救收視，有些藝人其實已經為這場show綵排過，不過收到風唐文龍係無綵排過，真係慘！而個蛋糕其實係用嚟扔陳敏之，因為咁啱撞正她生日的日子，結果台上一個中蛋糕，一個中奶茶，場面認真搞笑，希望佢哋唔好嬲喇，都係搞吓氣氛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/001147_bdaa0066585fc4c7bd29cb7379a84343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F001147_bdaa0066585fc4c7bd29cb7379a84343.jpg&h=a0cfae52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/001155_16c13a43a4d4ab10be1d7a279136f467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F001155_16c13a43a4d4ab10be1d7a279136f467.jpg&h=6c46908f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/001204_4ee59e2e0b319a1a1c423d92330c65b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F001204_4ee59e2e0b319a1a1c423d92330c65b5.jpg&h=8a7c7f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/001208_1538d1e008e3b3082009c988fe71ca1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F001208_1538d1e008e3b3082009c988fe71ca1a.jpg&h=964ac69f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edcbedee10abe8059939a2436e73194a17ae88ea","tid":521551,"uid":442,"like":269,"dislike":3,"score":266,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"掉壽包先谷到收視嫁嘛"},{"pid":"6cf5e660696b3971c214cb187156a42be09aa053","tid":521551,"uid":14486,"like":191,"dislike":3,"score":188,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"扔完都係冇尻人理呢陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf0b8687e316ee539f9315e471eeff7ca76a8a8","tid":521551,"uid":131686,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"edcbedee10abe8059939a2436e73194a17ae88ea","tid":521551,"uid":442,"like":269,"dislike":3,"score":266,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"掉壽包先谷到收視嫁嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"仍去啲空氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e326821f9afd0ec1bbcae5696934e02b92a3f377","tid":521551,"uid":131686,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4cf0b8687e316ee539f9315e471eeff7ca76a8a8","tid":521551,"uid":131686,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"edcbedee10abe8059939a2436e73194a17ae88ea","tid":521551,"uid":442,"like":269,"dislike":3,"score":266,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"掉壽包先谷到收視嫁嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"仍去啲空氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">掉</span>"},{"pid":"2027c1ac2117479b5168e5e2e54480cf291892ea","tid":521551,"uid":54104,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"點解會諗到呢啲方法救收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626857c32bf02199c0e2c271f88733c55bfe4726","tid":521551,"uid":156068,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"遲d可能出三點式救收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas